race.comment: CANDLEWICK (3) has her hoof on the till third-up from the gun draw. Loomed strongly along the inside before her condition gave out near the 100m with a tidy third over 1200m at this track. Gets the same set-up for this and expected to go close. CINSAULT (6) improving mare. Tagged the leader from the wide gate and had the race in her keeping a long way out with a comfortable win over 1400m at this track in BM72 class as fav. Heading in the right direction and has the talent to overcome the sticky gate. LA ROJA (7) gave 4.5kg to Sequista on resumption when she closed late to finish a narrow second over 1300m at Wyong. Handy mare who looks to have returned in good order. Expected to take a hand in the finish. BELLA CORAZON (15) frustrating mare who stays in the mix.
